/**
 * README for TodoListApp
 * 
 * This is a Java application that implements a Todo List using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts.
 * 
 * Features:
 * - Allows users to Create,Delete,Display,Mark as completed,Save,Load,Exit the console in a Todo List.
 * - Supports task prioritization and due dates.
 * - Provides functionality to mark tasks as completed.     
 * 
 * Usage:
 * 1. Run the TodoListApp.java file to start the application.
 * 2. Follow the on-screen instructions to interact with the Todo List.
 * 
 * Dependencies:
 * - This application requires Java Development Kit (JDK) version 8 or above.
 * 
 * Author: [Simery Kanna]
 * Date: [23-11-23]
 */
